{"tid":1623114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家放過狗鐵，對準共狗","createTime":"2019-10-04T18:26:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T19:05:58.000Z","uid":80972,"like":7,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a91f2dc0da5955f98013a487432297a73fa3e8c7","tid":1623114,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:26:18.000Z","msg":"狗鐵出賣港人，經過呢個幾月，已經受到教訓<br />\n畢竟狗鐵嘅錢係香港人俾，最後維修嘅錢都係香港人出，佢地d高層都唔會驚，d錢唔係佢地<br />\n<br />\n我地開始要對準嘅係中共政權，港共，奶共議員，<br />\n<br />\nPriority 1: 紅色企業<br />\n- 對抗共產機構滲透<br />\n- 減少紅色企業收入，盡力破壞中共財政收入<br />\n<br />\nPriority 2: 港共<br />\n- 港共狗官嘅罪唔使多講，記得仲有行會成員<br />\n- 好多非官守成員都係大公司主席/董事<br />\n<br />\n行會利益申報<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ceo.gov.hk/exco/chi/interests.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ceo.gov.hk%2Fexco%2Fchi%2Finterests.html&d=Bs0XXOgOekCAei%2FiISrrFltf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=a146bad1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ceo.gov.hk/exco/chi/interests.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPriority 3: 奶共議員<br />\n- 賣港求財，求名，求利，支持通過用緊急法通過蒙面法嘅議員都抵死<br />\n- 佢地一係自己有生意，一係就公司董事<br />\n<br />\n立會利益申報<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/cmi/yr16-20/reg_1620.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2Fchinese%2Fcmi%2Fyr16-20%2Freg_1620.htm&d=Bs0XXOgOekCAei%2FiISrrFltf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=aebd14d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/cmi/yr16-20/reg_1620.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n作為和理飛，我希望大家揾d民生相關嘅公司出黎抵制佢地。<br />\n<br />\n申利:唔鼓勵大家使用暴力去制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人<br />\n反抗!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cbff9cf2fa01fa2a87b7ebbbe29b99ea33ce737","tid":1623114,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a91f2dc0da5955f98013a487432297a73fa3e8c7","tid":1623114,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019